Double passage AQ
    1.  Same assessment criteria - relevance, explanation, evaluation and coherence
    2.  Read the question carefully and answer all questions posed to you
    3.  Discuss at least one point from each author
    4.  2 - 3 body paragraphs 
    5.  Also, remember, quality >> quantity
    6.  Search for points that both authors discussed and evaluate both concurrently
    7.  Recap - how to evaluate

Evaluation AQ paragraph
    1.  Author's point:
            biased
            overly critical
            rightly...
        Balance: global vs local
    
    2.  Explain Sg context
    
    3.  Apt examples

    4.  Balance
            Evaluation strategies
                majority vs minority
                ideal vs reality
                young vs old
            limitations/exceptions


